message.body: Got yr text from Harry's u sent to my old #! So glad u made it there. Why were u in west Hartford?!
Woops ;) I was on my way to Sharon to do Doubt so I stopped to see Brendan in Cabaret! He was incredible.
I have little or no service up here so sorry for the delayed responses! Hope you're well :)
I forgot u will be in Sharon. A truly beautiful place! How long r u there? Where is b doing cabaret?
B is in west Hartford. I'll be here 3 weeks :D
